The Global Voices Citizen Media Summit 2010 has been made possible thanks to
the generous support of the [MacArthur Foundation](http://www.macfound.org/),
[Google](http://google.com/), [Open Society Institute](http://www.soros.org/),
[Knight Foundation](http://www.knightfdn.org/) and
[Yahoo!](http://www.yahoo.com/).

Current major sponsors include MacArthur Foundation, Google, Open Society
Institute, Knight Foundation and Yahoo!

